**Key optimizations applied:**
- mmap + MADV_SEQUENTIAL for input files
- Parallel parsing (64 threads for lineitem)
- Direct SoA parsing (no row structs)
- std::from_chars for integers, manual date parsing (no mktime)
- Permutation-based sorting (sort indices, not full rows)
- Parallel column writes with 1MB buffers
- Dictionary encoding during parse (merged across threads)

